\mt1 TAITUS 
\mt2 Khe Por Taitus Ndi Khergi Gap 
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare. 
\ip Taitus, ana Zuda guma fhuvara. Ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, ruagiap, ana Por Fhe Bak…®me ana farasarigi Ňčaar, ana Porar kurav mba Ňčaara mbui. Por Taitus ndi Krit r…®g…®k…®rige t…®gim, ana niŇčgen ki. Ana niŇčgen kav, maaŇč guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba siosan ki, ana mben siosan Ňčaari gari. 
\ip Kha gap fharav khaŇč nzuai, mba Kritan ki nt…®…®ri, mben t…®vi nzerigi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, guma ana sios gari guman pan k…®r zav mbui, ana guigira t…®vi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Por zumgum mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®v…®v mbe suanga t…®vir Taitus ga nzuav, mba gumgi vuri kh…®v…®v mbe suanga t…®vi, mba mbigi vuri kh…®v…®v mbe suanga t…®vi, mba gumgir Ňčkaa kh…®v…®v mbe suanga t…®vi, mba Ňčaari gumgi, ana mbe suaŇčv mbe kh…®v…®rga t…®vir ana suaŇčgi. 
\ip Ana mpuu bunin, ana mba gavar khaŇč suaŇčgi, Taitus, ndu mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčrim, mbe wari t…®g…®p ndava bavira k…®v, t…®var vhuun harigi gumgir muuŇčri. Mbe fhura wari ga vheg…®p, wari daaŇč thari. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Taitus mba Krit r…®g…®k…®rigen guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gi havhar…®v, mbe t…®vi ndiv th…®gar maaŇčri. 
\p  
\v 1 Gu Por, gu Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara guma ma. Gu vh…®ra Zisas Krais farasarigi Ňčaara guma mbe ma. Ana na farasarav, na sarigim, gu Fhe Bak…®me won mbuigi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, gu mben kurkurav, mbe suaŇčrim, mbe guigira Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč kaŇčgip, ana t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Ro 16.25; Kor 1.27; 2 T 1.1; 1.9; 1 Pi 1.20\x*Gu mben kurkurarim, mbe khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®p, mbe Fhe Bak…®me rarg…® k…®rim, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®n mben n…®…®nga. Fhe Bak…®me fhum guarara, ana zumgum kha bigi ga muuŇčgi, ana fharav mba zazera mbara muuŇčgip ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®n nzan n…®…®n za suaŇčgi. Ana guiguigi guma fhuvara.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Ef 1.9-10; 1 Te 2.4; 1 T 1.1; 1.11; 2.3; 2 T 1.10; Ta 2.10; 3.4\x*Ana zumgum ana nduara mba tuga sarav, ana gumgi mbari farasegim, mbe mba buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai. Ana mba t…®va mbuav, ana za wo buna vhuueŇč ndi hiaŇč t…®gi. Fhe Bak…®me, ana taagiap nza ndi guma ma. Ana nzuaim, gu ana buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai Ňčaara ndigi. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Ro 1.7; 2 Ko 8.23; Ga 2.3; 2 T 1.2; 4.10\x*Taitus, gu kha gava khergiap ndu ndi mbai. Ndu nan kama guara fara muuŇčgi, ndu nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®vara muuŇčgiap ana khoth…®gi. Nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Krais Zisas, ana taagia nza ndi guma ma, ana ndu korar muuŇčv ndava m…®…®t…®gar ndun n…®…®Ňčrim, ndu k…®ri. 
\s1 Taitus sios gari gumgir pani vhuuiŇč ndi feg…®ri. 
\p  
\v 5 Gu ndu ndim Krit r…®g…®k…®rige t…®gim, ndu niŇčgen ki. Ndu k…®v, mba Ňčaari gu bigi mbari vh…®zgi, ndu nta ndiv th…®gar maaŇčri. Ndu nta ndiv th…®gar maaŇčv, ndu za mbe Ňčgui bak…®vir, gu mba fhum ndu suaŇčgi t…®var muuŇčv, ndu mben siosi gari gumgir pani ndi f…®ri.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2 T 2.24-26\x*\x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1 T 3.2-7\x*Ndu mbe ndi f…®r saŇčv, ndu mba gumgi gu mbigi n…®man t…®va mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgi fhuv guma, ana vh…®ra mbiga bavira man ki. Ndu mba khesharigi guma ndi f…®ri. Mba guman tari mbe vh…®ra Krais khoth…®g…®p, mbe Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi z…®n Ňčg…®rga fhu, mbe vh…®ra r…®…®r…®…®i t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®p, wari won ndegi gu ndegmbori nzuai buni daaŇčsurga fhu.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Wkp 10.9; 1 Ko 4.1; Ef 5.18; 1 Pi 5.2\x*Ndu kaŇčgi, sios gari guman pan, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara gari guma ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap ana rurur vhuuŇčra muuŇčri, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana muuŇčgi t…®va mbat…®k thueŇč gan…®nga fhu. Ana khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi thari, ana z…® bak…®me ki, ana tamtam mba gumgi gu mbigi gan…®nga. Ana vhemkora ndav shi thari. Ana pharar ŇčanŇčanin mb…®v ŇčanŇčan…® thari. Ana vhemkora ndav shiv harigi gumgi shog…® thari. Ana Ňčk…®…®a vh…®rve ndirga ne suaŇčv thaginen muuŇč thari.  
\v 8 Ana wo phenan zi gumgi, ana mben ndikndig…®p ana tuituigira mbe gan…®ri. Ana za t…®vir vhuuiŇčra vuzvug…®p, ana nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ana t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, za Fhe Bak…®men t…®va guara z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ana vh…®ra won k…®r…® t…®vi gu bigi, ana tuituigip nta gan…®ri.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt 1 T 1.10; 1.15; 2 T 1.13; 2.15; 4.3; Ta 2.1\x*Ana vh…®ra mbe ana kh…®vav, ana suaŇčgi buna vhuueŇč, ana nen suirav havhargiri. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgirga, ana buni guari, ana ntan mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®v…®rga, mbe mba buni khoth…®g…®rga. Ana maaŇč muuŇčv, vh…®ra mbe nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rga, mbe mba buni z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Ana maaŇč muuŇčv mba buni daasui gumgi, ana khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip mbe suanga, mbe guigira wari wo nzuai buni nta kaŇčgirga. 
\s1 Krit r…®g…®k…®rigen ki gumgi mbari, guigira Zisas khoth…®gim, gumgi vh…®rve mben nd…®knd…®gir farfagi. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 T 1.6; 4.7\x*Ndu sios gari gumgir pani vhuuiŇč ndi feg…®ri. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Kritan ki siosi vh…®rver ki gumgi, mbe buni daasui. Mbe fhura sh…®sh…®gi buni kh…®ni nzuav, fhura gumgi guiguigi. MaaŇč mbui gumgi vh…®rve, mbe ZudaiŇč ma. Mbe vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi ma. Mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap fooi t…®va z…®n vui.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Mt 23.14; Zo 10.12; 1 T 6.5; 2 T 3.6; 1 Pi 5.2\x*Mba gumgi t…®vir mbat…®gir muungeŇč vuzvugiap, mbe fhura gumgi guiguigap, mben t…®n mbe Ňčk…®…®a Ňčgi. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe mbe nzuav mbe kh…®vi t…®vi, nza mba t…®vir muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe mba t…®va mbuav, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir vh…®rve, mbe ana khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gi, mbe mben nd…®knd…®gir farfagi. Mbe mben farfav, vh…®ra mben mbik gu tarir nd…®knd…®gir farfagi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde mbe th…®v…®ri, mbe mba khesharigi bunin mbe suaŇč thari.  
\v 12 Fhum Kritan bigi kaŇčgi guma mbera khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄúMbe KritiŇč, mbe bigi guiguigi nt…®…®ri ma. Mbe guigira gumgi mbat…®gi ma. Mbe ruaŇčruaŇčgi s…®gi fara muuŇčgi. Mbe mba k…®vgi mb…®rgen ndikndigap, guigira vhukvhuga k…®vgi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 1 T 4.7; 2 T 4.2; 4.4; Ta 2.2\x*Kha buneŇč ne guigi guarara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap ndu kama havharara mbe suaŇčv, mbe t…®vi ndiv th…®gar maanga, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®rga.  
\v 14 Mbe fhura mba Zudain nz…®gi neŇčgi nzari kh…®ni, mbe khuarir nta r…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra k…®r buna vhuueŇč ga seg…®p, gumgi nduarira t…®gi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Mt 15.11; Ru 11.39-41; Ro 14.14; 14.20; 14.23; 1 Ko 6.12\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe nduarira, mbe Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgararga, mbar k…®rga bigi, nta vh…®ra Ňčgarigim, mbe nta ndi. Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me n…®man maaŇč muuŇčgip, t…®vi mbat…®gi z…®n Ňčg…®p, mbe Krais khoth…®gi fhu, mba big…®n the Ňčgararga tukt…®gi fhu. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, mben nd…®knd…®gi gum mben ndavi Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man nzaŇčnzaŇčgi.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Ro 1.28; 2 T 3.5; 3.8; 1 Zo 1.6; 2.4; Zu 1.4\x*Mben kaathoorin khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ Mben t…®vi khaŇč nzuai, mbe k…®r ana segi. Fhe Bak…®me guigira mbe vuzvugi fhu. Mbe buni daasui gumgi ma. Mbe t…®var vhuuŇč thuen muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. 
\c 2  
\s1 Nde gumgi vuri, nde Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi, nde tuituigip nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1 T 1.10; 6.3; 2 T 1.13; Ta 1.9\x*Ndu mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav mbe nzuai t…®vi, nta guigira Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®ri.  
\v 2 Ndu mba gumgi vuri ga suaŇčrim, mbe phara ŇčanŇčanin mb…®v ŇčanŇčan…® thari. Mbe wari wo mbui t…®vi, mbe tuituigip nta nd…®knd…®g…®p, mbe tuituigip wari wo mbui t…®vi gan…®ri. Mbe Zisas buna vhuueŇč, mbe guigira ne khoth…®g…®p, mbe guigira wari won ndavir harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®v, mbe guigira ne kaŇčgip, mbe khaŇč t…®g…®p th…®g…® havhargip simt…®gi ndiri. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt 1 T 3.11; 2 T 2.9-10; 1 Pi 3.3-4\x*Ndu vh…®ra mba mbigi vuri ga suaŇčrim, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi, mbe nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Mbe fhura sh…®sh…®g…®p buna thuen harigi gumgi ga s…®v buna thueŇč suaŇč thari. Mbe vh…®ra phara ŇčanŇčani mb…®rgeŇč nd…®knd…®g…® thari. Mbe t…®vir vhuuin muungen harigi nt…®…®ri kh…®v…®v mbe suaŇčri.  
\v 4 Mbe mbe suaŇčrim, mba mbigir Ňčkaa, mbe guigira wari won mani gu tari vuzvugi ne kaŇčgiri.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Ef 5.22; Kor 3.18; 1 T 2.11; 6.1; 1 Pi 3.1; 3.5\x*Mba mbigir Ňčkaa, mbe tuituigip piigip, nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p mbe Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man Ňčgarav k…®rga. Mbe vh…®ra tuituigip wari wo pheni gari t…®va kaŇčgip, mbe t…®var vhuun wari won mani gu tarir muuŇčv, mbe won mani piin k…®rga. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip mba t…®var muunga, guma the buni mbat…®gir Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč ga suanga fhu. 
\s1 Taitus t…®var vhuun muuŇčrim, mba gumgir Ňčkaa anan t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. 
\p  
\v 6 Ndu mba t…®vara, ndu mba gumgir Ňčkaa, ndu mbe nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, mbe tuituigip wari wo mbui t…®vi gan…®ri.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Ef 6.24; 1 T 4.12; 1 Pi 5.3\x*Ndu mba mbui t…®vi, ndu t…®var vhuuŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, ntan muuŇčrim, mba gumgi ndu gan…®p ndu z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ndu mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav mbe nzuai Ňčaarar muuŇčv, ndu mbe guiguigi thari. Ndu fhura sunuv Ňčg…®zi buni suaŇč thari. Fhuvara. Ndu zazera t…®vir vhuuiŇčra nd…®knd…®g…®p, buni vhuuiŇčra suaŇčri.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1 T 6.3; 2 T 3.14; 1 Pi 2.12; 2.15\x*Ndu buni vhuuiŇčra suanga, mba gumgi, mbe mba buni vhen t…®va mbat…®ga thueŇč gangirga fhu. Nzan pana gumgi, mbe vh…®ra, mbe buna mbat…®k thuen nza suaŇčgirga fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe won nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gir mbergirga. 
\s1 Fhura Ňčaara kh…®na mbui gumgi, mbe tuituigip wari gari gumgir pani nzuai buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 T 6.1-2\x*Ndu mba Ňčaara gumgi ga suaŇčrim, mbe wari wo gari gumgir pani piin k…®ri. Mbe mbe piin k…®v, Ňčaari vhuuiŇčra muuŇčrim, mben gumgir pani mbe mbui Ňčaari vuzvug…®ri. Mbe wari gari gumgir pani nzuai buni Ňčgar…®gar muuŇčv buni mbat…®gir mbe suaŇč thari.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Mt 5.16; Fi 2.15; Ta 1.3\x*Mbe wari gari gumgir panin bigi k…®m…® thari. Fhuvara. Mbe wari gari gumgir pani nzuai buni, mbe za nta z…®n Ňčg…®rim, mbe gari gumgir pani, mbe mbui t…®vi, mbe guigira ntan ndikndigirga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe mbui bigi mba gumgi nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rga, mbe nza nzuai buni ndiv vun kuamkuav z…® bak…®men ntan n…®…®nga. Mba buni nta guigira Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč ma. Ana taagiap nza ndi guma ma. 
\s1 Nza Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®p, Krais taagi zir…®rga tugar rarg…®p k…®rga. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Zo 1.9; Ro 5.15; 1 Pi 5.12\x*Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®men kora muumbar, ana k…®rar h…®gi. Ana za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndigirga tukt…®gi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Ro 6.19; Ef 1.4; Kor 1.22; 1 Te 4.7; 1 Zo 2.16\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®men kora muumbar, ana khuen nza kh…®vi, nza k…®r Fhe Bak…®me s…®rga tukt…®gi fhu. Nza vh…®ra kha nuiana vuzvugi mbat…®gi, tharga. Ana vh…®ra khuen nza kh…®vi, nza tuituigi piigip t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p za Fhe Bak…®men t…®va guara z…®n Ňčg…®rga. KhueŇč guigira, nza kha nuiana gumgi r…®gar ki. Fhe Bak…®men kora muumbar ana khuen nza kh…®vigi, nza Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Ko 1.7; Fi 3.20; Kor 3.4; Hi 9.28; 1 Zo 3.2\x*Nza ana t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®p, nza khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip mba big…®na vhuuŇč gan…® saŇčv, nen ndikndigip nen rarg…®p k…®rga. Nza Zisas Krais rargap ki, ana ŇčkasŇčkagi Fhe Bak…®me ma. Ana taagia nza ndi guma ma. Ana Fhe Bak…®men s…®…®n vhuuŇč gum, ana vhava Ňčaara bak…®me, ana ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me phorg…®p k…®rar h…®rga.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Kis 19.5; Lo 4.20; 7.6; 14.2; Sng 130.8; Ese 37.23; Ga 1.4; 1 Pi 2.9\x*Krais ana taagiap nza ndir zav won tuma fekh…®ngip, nza muuŇčgim, nza muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®zgim, nza guigira Ňčgarav, nza ana gumgi gu mbigi ki. Nza khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip anan t…®vir vhuuiŇč z…®n Ňčg…®rga. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 T 4.12; 2 T 4.2\x*Ndu zazera kha bunin mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčri. Ndu mbe nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, mbe kha buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ndu vh…®ra kama havharan mba buni daasui gumgi ga suaŇčv, mben t…®vi ndi th…®gar maaŇčri. Ndu fhura mba gumgi gan…®rim, mbe ndu buni farfav, nta suaŇč thari. 
\c 3  
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuuŇč guarara nza muuŇčgim, nza t…®vir vhuuin muunga. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Ro 13.1-7; Kor 1.10; Hi 13.21; 1 Pi 2.13-14\x*Ndu kha gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčrim, mbe Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani gum Ňčgui gari gumgir pani, mbe mben piin k…®v, mbe nzuai buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Mbe zazera Ňčaari vhuuiŇčra muun saŇčv k…®ri.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Ef 4.2; 4.31; Fi 4.5; Kor 3.12; 2 T 2.24-25\x*Mbe buni mbat…®gir guma the suaŇč thari. Mbe buni ga suaŇčv wari daaŇč thari. Mbe zazera mbarara k…®v, t…®vir vhuuin za kha gumgi gu mbigir muuŇčri. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Ko 6.11; Ef 2.1-2; 5.8; Kor 1.21; 1 Pi 4.3\x*Ndu kaŇčgi, nza fhum mbara muuŇčgi, nza nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki fhu, nza buni daasui. Satan nza guigim, nza Fhe Bak…®men tuav z…®n vui fhu. Nza kha t…®va muuŇčgi, nza fhura ndavi khavav mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir Ňčaara gumgi kav, ndavi khavav mbark…®rga vuzvugi z…®n vui. Nza fhura vhegap, harigi gumgi ga nzuav ndavi mbar…®gi tuav, nza ana z…®n vui. Gumgi panan nza kim, nza bevbevira panan harigi gumgi ga ki. 
\p  
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 3:4-5 \xt 1 T 2.3; Ta 1.3; 2.11\x*\x - \xo 3:4-5 \xt Zo 3.3-5; Ro 11.6; Ef 5.26; 2 T 1.9; 1 Pi 3.21\x*Fhe Bak…®me ana taagiap nza ndi guma ma. Ana guigira won ndavar nza n…®…®Ňčgiap, nza kora muuŇčgiap, ana t…®var vhuuŇčra nza mbui. Ana mba t…®va ndi k…®ra kh…®ngiap, ana taagiap nza ndi. Ana nza muuŇčgi t…®var vhuuŇč thueŇč nd…®knd…®gap, ana mba t…®var nza muuŇčgiap taagiap nza ndigi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana won kora muumbarar, ana taagiap nza ndigi. Ana nza ndigap, nza ruagim, nza ntigera niamuuŇč ruagi tara fara muuŇčgim, ana Ňäina Ňäaar t…®var kaman nza n…®…®Ňčgi.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Jol 2.28; FG 2.17-18; 2.33; Ro 5.5\x*Taagia nza ndi guma Zisas Kraisan Ňčaara panan, Fhe Bak…®me khaŇč t…®gap won Ňäina Ňäaara siav nza suagi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Ro 3.24; 8.23-24; Ga 2.16; Ta 2.11\x*Krais nza kora muuŇčgip, nza muuŇčgim, nza Fhe Bak…®me n…®man t…®var vhuuaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ki. Mba t…®vara Fhe Bak…®me mba zazera mbara muuŇčgip ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndir zav nza farasarigim, nza mba k…®r…® t…®va rarga wari ki.  
